OL,3,CSister of M62 bombing victim says she
OL,4,Cremains 'devastated' by his death
OL,6,FMs Norton said her family was
OL,7,F"completely devastated by Terence's
OL,8,Fkilling but there is no hate in me".
OL,10,FRemembering her brother, she added:
OL,11,F"He was always good fun, laughing and
OL,12,Fjoking.
OL,14,F"But above all he was kind and that's
OL,15,Fnot just something a sister would say
OL,16,Fanyway.
OL,18,F"It's what his friends and colleagues
OL,19,Fin the army said as well."
