OL,3,CSister of M62 bombing victim says she
OL,4,Cremains 'devastated' by his death
OL,6,FMs Norton said her brother had done
OL,7,Ftwo tours of duty in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fand her family was worried about his
OL,9,Fsafety.
OL,11,FShe added: "But we never thought
OL,12,Fanything would happen when he was on
OL,13,Fleave. He never planned to be
OL,14,Ftravelling by coach because he just
OL,15,Fdidn't like it.
OL,17,F"But there was a train strike and the
OL,18,Fcoach was laid on."
