OL,3,CSister of M62 bombing victim says she
OL,4,Cremains 'devastated' by his death
OL,6,FShe said: "My mum and dad, Terence and
OL,7,Fmy two sisters Kathleen and Barbara
OL,8,Fwere so close and this devastated us
OL,9,Fall.
OL,11,FMs Norton added: "It will be hard at
OL,12,Fthe memorial service but having the
OL,13,Fsupport of others who have gone
OL,14,Fthrough the same experience will be a
OL,15,Fgreat help.
OL,17,F"I will always keep Terence's name and
OL,18,Fmemory alive."
